</head><body><table border=0 align=center width=80%><tr><td class=textbody><center><h1>Buckler of Insight</h1><br>by Tarrath Silvermoon</center><br><div align="center">
  <center>
  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="573" id="AutoNumber1">
    <tr>
      <td width="573">
  <p align="center">This quest, also known as the 'Test of the Emerald Tear', 
  takes place in the Temple of Veeshan by talking to Lendiniara. 

  </p>

  <hr noshade>

      </div>

  <p align="left">Talk to
  <a href="javascript:;" onclick="MM_openBrWindow('lendiniara.jpg','lendiniara','width=409,height=421')">
  Lendiniara the Keeper</a> (-1065, +1125) within the West wing of the Temple of 
  Veeshan.</p>
  <blockquote>
    <p>You say, 'what test of the emerald tear'</p>
    <p>Lendiniara the Keeper says 'The emerald tear of Veeshan entrusted to the 
    cursed one. Return this tear to me so I may return the powers of an ancient 
    shield. Three symbols you must also seek. Emerald like the tear, one kissed 
    by the flames of the elder wurms and one made of the ancient wyverns 
    venomous poison.</p>
  </blockquote>
  <p align="left">The tears are obtained from Dozekar the Cursed, the boss of 
  the Halls of Testing in the Temple of Veeshan. Once you have all of the items, 
  go back to Lendiniara and hand her all four items. You will be rewarded with 
  the Buckler of Insight.</p>
  <p align="left"> </p>

